{"tid":1097164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老爸要繼母扮狗、天天睡不同人...17歲女力挺！淫亂豪宅生活曝光","createTime":"2019-04-08T08:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T19:59:54.000Z","uid":32511,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0dca39d47f988d0211bf1dd080e7b18b185b0c7a","tid":1097164,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"澳洲46歲的菸草大亨貝農（Travers Beynon）以無下限的淫亂生活出名，例如每晚都會跟超過3名女性一起睡覺等等，他的17歲女兒露西亞娜（Lucciana Beynon）近日受訪時為父親辯護，他表示，家中的生活的確很瘋狂，但她都能夠接受，而且是父親管教嚴格，培養她擁有正確的價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n貝農的奢華「糖果店豪宅」（Candyshop Mansion）位在澳洲昆士蘭的黃金海岸地區，時常會舉辦各種大尺度淫亂趴，更常常拍照炫耀開趴的情景。於此同時，他的4個孩子、老婆和多名女友也都一起住在這間房子裡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjnpPSZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjnpPSZ.jpg&h=66ff3dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n也因此，許多人更加好奇在這棟常辦淫趴的豪宅長大是什麼狀況，露西亞娜表示，「其實沒有任何事情是會嚇到我的，我爸對於這些淫亂趴抱持開放態度，我接受這一切，我愛他原本的樣子」，爸爸的確是有很多女友，但大家相處融洽，就像真正的一家人。她認為，這種多P是的關係是可以接受的，只要大家都是情投意合的成年人就好。<br />\n<br />\n不過，貝農的荒唐生活也招致許多批評，有一次他讓老婆扮成狗，錄影PO在IG上，讓許多人罵他是「性別歧視」、「沙文主義」等等，但露西亞娜替爸爸辯護提到，「我覺得有人說他物化女性是很可笑的事情」。<br />\n<br />\n由於在這樣的環境下長大，讓露西亞娜變得很成熟，她覺得這是很棒的事情，且即便生在富裕的家庭，父親也從來不寵壞小孩，「他思想意外的很老舊，對我們比其他的爸爸都還嚴格，他教我們有禮貌、尊重、展現成熟態度並努力工作，這才造就了我們今天的樣子」。<br />\n<br />\n露西亞娜現在是一名模特兒，在IG上已經有超過6.7萬人追蹤，她的夢想是成為維多利亞秘密內衣秀的超模，之後將會搬到美國追求夢想，之後也打算把賺來的錢投資到家族事業中。"},{"pid":"76d8d629b64e25fc16720b6c4f8c8af633f54808","tid":1097164,"uid":47303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:11:20.000Z","msg":"快點強姦我"},{"pid":"741ac8a801a8442008e14df78f34405c18b626f8","tid":1097164,"uid":75994,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"有一次他讓老婆扮成狗，錄影PO在IG上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個post好似差d野"},{"pid":"92f97513fe6dd434c74d2d392836adb4610769ff","tid":1097164,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odhUjht.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodhUjht.png&h=12f3742e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KGmRt3N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKGmRt3N.png&h=a47ae700&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ae1d765109aca2b7860beadf50529d4c1c9fdc3","tid":1097164,"uid":33821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:24:09.000Z","msg":"有錢係咁架啦 咪酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98782a9d3db1d3839dd6ab7ac36779682176fe7e","tid":1097164,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"好想俾佢個女騎"},{"pid":"11b5261f1847ee39875f59fef73c70602938cf07","tid":1097164,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"想做佢女婿 再參加party"},{"pid":"5f295772828c54772a4be2d352cccd13e6f1721d","tid":1097164,"uid":148332,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"11b5261f1847ee39875f59fef73c70602938cf07","tid":1097164,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T08:37:14.000Z","msg":"想做佢女婿 再參加party"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"到時佢個女叫你扮狗"},{"pid":"7ae1371b94a3d8d21dcc79fed3f8dda221a551d6","tid":1097164,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"有錢扮狗<br />\n但無錢要做狗<br />\n你揀邊樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c191b8dc38440dc917fe5eb05b37aa424ec3743","tid":1097164,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T19:19:30.000Z","msg":"第二個有錢都唔一定教到個女咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6885691b4eacc1c4fce8f0fe2e496e1dc3f338b","tid":1097164,"uid":241021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7ae1371b94a3d8d21dcc79fed3f8dda221a551d6","tid":1097164,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T09:06:36.000Z","msg":"有錢扮狗<br />\n但無錢要做狗<br />\n你揀邊樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T19:49:26.000Z","msg":"做狗，即本身係狗，無問題。<br />\n扮狗，即本身係人，有尊嚴問題。"},{"pid":"849aed89a9186d720f7fb04a04ef9ef254c6a1a2","tid":1097164,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T19:59:54.000Z","msg":"呀女有無扮狗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}